\begin{block}{Key Findings}
\begin{itemize}
\item Geometry stable under severe marker loss.
\item kNN topology degrades predictably.
\item Correspondence-free validation feasible.
\item PCA remains most stable baseline in $n \ll p$.
\end{itemize}
